# Architecture

Always prefer:

- Single Source of Truth
- One owner per responsibility
- Stable state
- Stable effects
- Minimal Context Providers

Never duplicate:

- Controllers
- State
- Lifecycle
- Business logic

Before creating a new Context, Provider, Controller or Hook,

verify whether an existing one can own the responsibility.

Refactor instead of duplicating.
